## Limitations

The findings are based on available literature and may not encompass all aspects of adaptive leadership in irregular warfare. The dynamic nature of military operations means that new strategies and insights are continually emerging. Additionally, the focus on military sources may limit the applicability of findings to non-military contexts of irregular warfare. Further research could explore adaptive leadership in civilian-led irregular warfare scenarios.